snippet.title: Lab Rat - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Need a laugh? Lab Rat is a satirical adventure staring a metrics-obsessed AI who will monitor, profile, and entertain you as you progress through over a hundred satisfying and genre-bending puzzles. 

Full Release is coming to PC and Xbox in 2022!

Join the closed beta right now at labrat.study!

Follow the game on twitter: https://twitter.com/direGoldfish
